&lt;p&gt;I will be rebalancing on the first trading day of the month.&lt;/p&gt;</content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html">I recently decided to run a systematic momentum strategy on ASX listed equities within the All Ordinaries (excluding the ASX 100). I figured that the market was running pretty hot and there really wasn’t anything that could go wrong. brrr</summary></entry><entry><title type="html">First crypto rotation</title><link href="http://localhost:4000/2020/12/14/crpytomomo.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="First crypto rotation" /><published>2020-12-14T19:40:00+11:00</published><updated>2020-12-14T19:40:00+11:00</updated><id>http://localhost:4000/2020/12/14/crpytomomo</id><content type="html" xml:base="http://localhost:4000/2020/12/14/crpytomomo.html">&lt;p&gt;I have been out of the crypto game for a while but recently found myself reinterested after catching up with someone I hadn’t seen for a while. The timing of such discussions worked well, as recently, I had been exploring systematic momentum strategies on equities.&lt;/p&gt;

